## Типографика

```css
.mm-block .mm-h2 { font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.25; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin: 0 0 14px; }
.mm-block .mm-h3 { font-size: clamp(19px, 2.8vw, 26px); line-height: 1.35; font-weight: 650; letter-spacing: -.01em; margin: 0 0 14px; }
.mm-block .mm-h4 { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.35; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 8px; }
.mm-block .mm-intro-text { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: #333333; }
.mm-block .mm-card-desc  { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: #555555; }
.mm-block .mm-muted      { font-size: 13px; color: #999999; }
.mm-block .mm-card-meta  { font-size: 13px; color: #999999; }
```

---

## Структура страницы

```css
.mm-block .mm-container   { max-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }
.mm-block .mm-section     { padding: 26px 0; }
.mm-block .mm-section--soft { padding: 22px 20px; border-radius: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); }
.mm-block .mm-divider     { height: 1px; background: #e5e5e5; margin: 26px 0; }
```

