## Компоненты

### Liquid Glass карточка (`.mm-glass`)
```css
.mm-block .mm-glass {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.62); border-radius: 20px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.06), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.6) inset;
  backdrop-filter: blur(22px) saturate(180%);
}
```

### Кнопки
```css
/* Primary — зелёный градиент */
.mm-block .mm-btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px; padding: 13px 20px; border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4AE580, #20CCBE); color: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid transparent; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;
}
.mm-block .mm-btn-primary:hover { background: #000; color: #fff; }

/* Secondary — светлый */
.mm-block .mm-btn-secondary {
  /* те же базовые стили */
  background: #F0F0F0; border-color: #e5e5e5; color: #000000;
}
/* Secondary внутри .mm-cta */
.mm-block .mm-cta .mm-btn-secondary { background: transparent; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color: #fff; }

/* Ссылка-карточка */
.mm-block .mm-card-link { color: #20CCBE; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: auto; }
```

### Карточка контента (`.mm-card`)
```css
.mm-block .mm-services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 16px; }
.mm-block .mm-card { padding: 20px 18px 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.mm-block .mm-card-top { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.mm-block .mm-card-ico {
  width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4AE580, #20CCBE);
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  color: #fff; font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 46px;
}
```
> Иконка + заголовок `.mm-h4` + мета `.mm-card-meta` + текст `.mm-card-desc` + ссылка `.mm-card-link`

### Stat-strip (контактные плитки)
```css
.mm-block .mm-stat-strip { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 14px; }
.mm-block .mm-stat-card  { padding: 18px 16px 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
                            justify-content: space-between; min-height: 110px;
                            overflow-wrap: break-word; min-width: 0; }
/* Кликабельная карточка */
.mm-block a.mm-stat-card { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; cursor: pointer; }
.mm-block a.mm-stat-card:hover { border-color: rgba(74,229,128,0.55); }
.mm-block .mm-stat-ico { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
                         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4AE580, #20CCBE);
                         display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
                         color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0; }
```
> Stat-strip всегда использует `minmax(0,1fr)` — не просто `1fr` — чтобы длинный текст не растягивал колонку.

### CTA-блок
```css
.mm-block .mm-cta { background: #2C2C2C; color: #fff; padding: 26px 22px; border-radius: 22px; }
.mm-block .mm-cta h3 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0 0 8px; }
.mm-block .mm-cta p  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); margin: 0; }
```

### FAQ
```css
.mm-block .mm-faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
.mm-block .mm-faq-item { padding: 18px 16px; }
.mm-block .mm-faq-question { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 6px; }
.mm-block .mm-faq-answer   { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: #555555; }
.mm-block .mm-faq-answer a { color: #20CCBE; }
```

### Бейджи
```css
.mm-block .mm-badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; }
.mm-block .mm-stat-badge {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 14px;
  color: #2C2C2C; background: #F3F3F3; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
}
.mm-block .mm-stat-badge .mm-badge-ico {
  width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: #44CC55;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff;
}
```

